Package: hydat
Type: Package
Title: To quickly arrange and analyze data downloaded from the Government of Canada Hydat database.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("David", "Tavernini", email = "taverninid@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
url: https://github.com/dtavern/hydat
bugreports: https://github.com/dtavern/hydat/issues
Description: A few functions in this package allow for a quick manipulation of hydat data into "long" format. Additional functions
allow for quick calculation of mean monthly discharge, generation of hydrographs and rating curves, and to also calculate rating curve
equations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    tidyverse
